plot_house <- function(house_percent, house_total, total, df) {
   ordered <- df[order(-df[[house_percent]], -df[[house_total]]),]
    #small <- small[order(-small$percent_brobnar, -small$brobnar_total),]
     
   ordered <- head(ordered, total)
   
   ordered$name_words <- factor(ordered$name_words, levels = ordered$name_words)
   
   p <-ggplot(data=ordered, aes(x=name_words, y=ordered[[house_total]])) +
      geom_bar(stat="identity", width=.5, fill="tomato3") + 
      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle=65, vjust=0.6))
      
   return(p)
}
